<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1335 gu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>mārggasira sukla śaptamiyu guruvāramunā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁḍu niḷadēvimahādēvi tanaku Abhiṣṭārttasiddhigā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nu śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki Ubhayadhupalāṁdunu
<lb n="5"/>nityamunnu mruguveṭṭanu naruvapediyakkaku śrī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhaṁḍaramaṁdu nālugu māḍalu padmanidhigāṁ beṭi ku
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁcaprasādamu dīnikiṁ beṭiri I prasādhamu bhujiṁci I
<lb n="8"/>kolupu Ācaṁdrārkastayigānu koluvaṁgaladu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> yi mahadēvi ta
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lli yirāmudusali tanaku Abhīṣṭārttasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nāthuniki dupakālamaṁdu Oka Ālavaṭṭamu nityamunnu <unclear>pa</unclear>
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rimāṟanu baṁḍḍāra siṁgannakuṁ beṭenu nityamunnu tirumajyena
<lb n="12" break="no"/>mu garayā tecipeṭṭanu babbāyimādannakuṁ beṭṭenu śrībhaṁḍḍāra
<lb n="13" break="no"/>maṁdu yeni<unclear>mi</unclear>di māḍalu padmanidhigāṁ beṭṭi reṁḍu ku<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>calu prasā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>damu vrittigāṁ goni peṭṭenu vīru Ī prasādamu bhujiṁci yī
<lb n="15"/>kolupu Ācaṁdrarkastayigānu koluvaṁgalāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dha
<lb n="16" break="no"/>rmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

